languages.text: "Я вижу много эмоций и вздохов по прошедшим дням, но не вижу компетентности. В дальнейшем я не собираюсь полагаться ни на твои суждения, ни на "заведенные порядки".
"I have seen plenty of sentiment and handwringing in recent days, but very little competence. I have no plans to rely on your judgement or your 'tried and tested procedures' in the future."
languages.original_text: "Я вижу много эмоций и вздохов по прошедшим дням, но не вижу компетентности. В дальнейшем я не собираюсь полагаться ни на твои суждения, ни на "заведенные порядки".

languages.text: “最近这段时间，我只看到了没完没了的不满与抱怨，没看到什么可靠的表现。我以后不打算听信你的判断，也不打算依靠你所谓的‘久经时间考验的既定规矩’。”
languages.original_text: "I have seen plenty of sentiment and handwringing in recent days, but very little competence. I have no plans to rely on your judgement or your 'tried and tested procedures' in the future."

languages.text: «He visto muchas emociones y apretones de manos últimamente, pero muy poca competencia. No tengo intención de confiar en su juicio ni en sus "procedimientos de eficacia asegurada" de aquí en adelante».
languages.original_text: "I have seen plenty of sentiment and handwringing in recent days, but very little competence. I have no plans to rely on your judgement or your 'tried and tested procedures' in the future."

traits.locale_text: «He visto muchas emociones y apretones de manos últimamente, pero muy poca competencia. No tengo intención de confiar en su juicio ni en sus "procedimientos de eficacia asegurada" de aquí en adelante».

languages.text: 「ここ数日、感情的な心を痛めるような発言はたくさん目にしたが、適正はほとんど感じられなかった。私は今後、お前の判断や『試行錯誤を重ねた手順』に頼るつもりはない」
languages.original_text: "I have seen plenty of sentiment and handwringing in recent days, but very little competence. I have no plans to rely on your judgement or your 'tried and tested procedures' in the future."

traits.locale_text: 「ここ数日、感情的な心を痛めるような発言はたくさん目にしたが、適正はほとんど感じられなかった。私は今後、お前の判断や『試行錯誤を重ねた手順』に頼るつもりはない」

languages.text: "Ich habe in den letzten Tagen viele Meinungen gehört, viel Händeringen gesehen, aber herzlich wenig Kompetenz. Ich habe nicht vor, mich in Zukunft weiter auf Euer Urteil oder Eure 'bewährten Verfahren' zu verlassen."
languages.original_text: "I have seen plenty of sentiment and handwringing in recent days, but very little competence. I have no plans to rely on your judgement or your 'tried and tested procedures' in the future."

traits.locale_text: "Ich habe in den letzten Tagen viele Meinungen gehört, viel Händeringen gesehen, aber herzlich wenig Kompetenz. Ich habe nicht vor, mich in Zukunft weiter auf Euer Urteil oder Eure 'bewährten Verfahren' zu verlassen."

languages.text: « Sensiblerie et incompétence semblent avoir pris le pas sur l'efficacité de mon équipage, ces derniers temps. À l'avenir, je me passerai allègrement de votre avis et de vos sacro-saintes "procédures". »
languages.original_text: "I have seen plenty of sentiment and handwringing in recent days, but very little competence. I have no plans to rely on your judgement or your 'tried and tested procedures' in the future."

traits.locale_text: « Sensiblerie et incompétence semblent avoir pris le pas sur l'efficacité de mon équipage, ces derniers temps. À l'avenir, je me passerai allègrement de votre avis et de vos sacro-saintes "procédures". »

languages.text: "Şu son günlerde sürekli laf işitip sızlanma duyuyorum fakat liyakatten eser yok. Bundan böyle senin muhakemene yahut 'kurallara bağlı prosedürlerin'e bel bağlamayacağım."

traits.locale_text: "Şu son günlerde çok laf duydum ama liyakatten eser yok. Bundan böyle senin muhakemene yahut 'kurallara bağlı prosedürlerine' bel bağlamayacağım."
